==English==
{{wikipedia|Abstraction (disambiguation)|Abstraction}}

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abstraccyone}}; either from {{der|en|frm|abstraction}} or from {{der|en|ML.|abstrāctiō|t=separation}}, from {{der|en|la|abstrahō|t=draw away}}. Equivalent to {{af|en|abstract|-ion}}.

